data.description: Welcome Home! This adorable 4 bed, 3 bath, 2 car garage home in popular Hickory Hill is ready for its new owner! Home features a bright two-story entry, living room, dining room, and kitchen overlooking the family room - complete with fireplace and patio access. Don't miss the gorgeous engineered hardwood floors featured throughout the main living spaces of the home. And kitchen boasts white cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. All 4 bedrooms are above grade  and primary features an en suite and walk-in closet! Plus, enjoy the lower level flex space and laundry with utility sink. Relax in your fully fenced back yard, complete with patio, mature vegetation, pond and storage shed. Walk to local schools restaurants and shopping. Call today for your private tour!
